---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy · Guiding Winds Unplug';
const description =
  'How we collect, use, and protect the information you share when you inquire about a voyage or sign up for our newsletter.';
const updated = '2026-05-17';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="bg-bone text-primary">
    <div class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto px-7 lg:px-0 pt-24 pb-32 lg:pt-32">
      <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.6875rem] font-semibold text-primary/65 mb-4">
        Privacy
      </p>
      <h1
        class="font-display text-primary leading-[1] tracking-[-0.025em] font-light"
        style="font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw + 1rem, 3.5rem); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;"
      >
        Privacy policy.
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body-sm text-[0.8125rem] text-primary/45 mt-4">Last updated {updated}</p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 font-body-lg text-[1.0625rem] leading-[1.7] text-primary/65">
        <p>
          We collect the information you send us when you inquire about a
          voyage, hold a cabin, or subscribe to our newsletter. That includes
          your name, email, phone (if you share it), preferred travel dates,
          party size, and any notes you write us. We use it to reply to your
          inquiry, confirm cabin holds, and send the email sequences you opt
          into. We do not sell or share it with third parties for marketing.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-h2 text-primary leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] font-normal mt-12" style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72;">
          What we collect
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 list-disc list-outside pl-6">
          <li>Contact info you submit through our inquiry, newsletter, or hold-cabin forms</li>
          <li>Trip preferences you share (week, party size, dietary needs, notes)</li>
          <li>Anonymous traffic data via Plausible - no cookies, no personal identifiers, no cross-site tracking</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-h2 text-primary leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] font-normal mt-12" style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72;">
          Where it lives
        </h2>
        <p>
          Form submissions are sent server-side to our CRM (GoHighLevel,
          operated by Dodie's business account). Our analytics platform is
          Plausible, a privacy-first analytics service that does not use
          cookies and stores aggregated traffic data only.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-h2 text-primary leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] font-normal mt-12" style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72;">
          Your rights
        </h2>
        <p>
          Email <a href="mailto:dodie@guidingwinds-unplug.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">dodie@guidingwinds-unplug.com</a> any time to:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 list-disc list-outside pl-6">
          <li>See what we have on file for you</li>
          <li>Update or correct anything</li>
          <li>Delete your record entirely</li>
          <li>Unsubscribe from any sequence (there's also a link in every email)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-h2 text-primary leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] font-normal mt-12" style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72;">
          Cookies
        </h2>
        <p>
          We do not set tracking cookies. We use one strictly necessary
          cookie to remember your dismissal of the newsletter strip. Plausible
          analytics is cookie-less by design.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-h2 text-primary leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] font-normal mt-12" style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72;">
          Security
        </h2>
        <p>
          Forms post over HTTPS. CRM credentials are stored in encrypted
          environment variables on Cloudflare Pages and rotated annually.
          We do not store payment information on the site - deposits run
          through Stripe and we never see your card number.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-h2 text-primary leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] font-normal mt-12" style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72;">
          Updates to this policy
        </h2>
        <p>
          If we change the policy materially, we'll update the date at the
          top and email anyone who has an active record with us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
